```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Тестируем связку Forms → n8n → Tilda</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #333;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e9ecef 100%);
            padding: 20px;
        }

        article {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            padding: 60px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(57, 0, 132, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            color: #390084;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 2em;
            color: #E9007C;
            margin: 40px 0 20px 0;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #00C8FF;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .highlight-block {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(57, 0, 132, 0.05) 0%, rgba(0, 200, 255, 0.05) 100%);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border-left: 5px solid #390084;
        }

        ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding-left: 0;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }

        ul li {
            padding: 15px 20px;
            margin: 12px 0;
            background: white;
            border-left: 4px solid #00C8FF;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        ul li:hover {
            transform: translateX(10px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(233, 0, 124, 0.2);
            border-left-color: #E9007C;
        }

        ul li:before {
            content: "✦";
            color: #E9007C;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-right: 15px;
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }

        strong {
            color: #390084;
            font-weight: 600;
            background: linear-gradient(120deg, rgba(233, 0, 124, 0.1) 0%, rgba(0, 200, 255, 0.1) 100%);
            padding: 2px 6px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        p {
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            color: #555;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            article {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 1.8em;
            }

            h2 {
                font-size: 1.5em;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <article>
        <h1>Тестируем связку Forms → n8n → Tilda</h1>

        <div class="highlight-block">
            <ul>
                <li>Пункт 1</li>
                <li>Пункт 2</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <h2>Подзаголовок H2</h2>

        <p>Заключительный текст.</p>
    </article>
</body>
</html>
```
